data.text:
A unique piece that manages to capture the essence of one of the oldest distilleries in Mexico in a work that sports 135 European crystals, in collaboration with the Preciosa brand and that are placed one by one by Mexican hands in Los Altos de Jalisco.

Slightly sweet flavor with low alcoholic impact, sapid with a certain oily texture, which provides a permanently soft and harmonious palate.
